      <title>饮酒者感到压力，干邑白兰地被淘汰，龙舌兰酒流行起来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/cognac-s-out-and-tequila-s-in-as-drinkers-feel-the-pinch</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利 (Morgan Stanley) 分析师表示，美国消费者正从干邑白兰地转向龙舌兰酒，这强化了该银行的观点，即客户应该出售人头马君度酒业 (Remy Cointreau SA) 的股票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-09/cognac-s-out-and-tequila-s-in-as-drinkers-feel-the-pinch</guid>
